<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Free Medicare Tools & Resources | The Health Experts Insurance</title>
<meta name="description" content="Free Medicare calculators, guides, and tools for South Florida seniors. Compare plans, calculate IRMAA surcharges, find your enrollment window, and more — bilingual EN/ES.">
<link rel="canonical" href="https://www.healthexps.com/resources">
<link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://www.healthexps.com/resources">
<link rel="alternate" hreflang="es" href="https://www.healthexps.com/es/recursos">
<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
html,body{overflow-x:hidden;max-width:100%;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;background:#faf9fd;color:#1a1a2e;}
a{text-decoration:none;color:inherit;}

.topbar{background:#452068;padding:10px 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
.topbar-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;}
.topbar-phone{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);font-weight:600;}
.topbar-lang{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);}
.topbar-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
.btn-wa{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:#25D366;color:white;padding:7px 14px;border-radius:50px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;}
.btn-consult{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:#ff1090;color:white;padding:7px 16px;border-radius:50px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;}
.lang-wrap{display:flex;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border-radius:50px;overflow:hidden;margin-left:8px;}
.lb{padding:5px 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);cursor:pointer;border:none;background:transparent;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;}
.lb.active{background:white;color:#452068;border-radius:50px;}

.header{background:white;padding:0 40px;height:68px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(69,32,104,0.08);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;}
.brand img{height:50px;width:auto;}
.brand-fallback{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#452068;}
.header-phone{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;background:#452068;color:#fff;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:50px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;}

.breadcrumb{background:white;border-bottom:1px solid #f0ecf8;padding:12px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;}
.breadcrumb a{color:#452068;font-weight:500;}
.breadcrumb a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}
.breadcrumb span{margin:0 8px;color:#d1c4e9;}

/* HERO */
.hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#311549 0%,#452068 60%,#6b2fa0 100%);padding:56px 24px 80px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.hero::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-2px;left:0;right:0;height:60px;background:#faf9fd;clip-path:ellipse(55% 100% at 50% 100%);}
.hero-eyebrow{display:inline-block;background:rgba(255,16,144,0.2);border:1px solid rgba(255,16,144,0.4);border-radius:50px;padding:6px 16px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#ff9fd4;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;}
.hero h1{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,46px);font-weight:900;color:white;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:14px;}
.hero h1 em{font-style:normal;color:#ff1090;}
.hero-sub{font-size:17px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);max-width:580px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.7;}

/* MAIN */
.main{max-width:1060px;margin:0 auto;padding:56px 20px 80px;}

/* SECTION HEADER */
.section-header{margin-bottom:28px;}
.section-eyebrow{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#ff1090;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:8px;}
.section-title{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:700;color:#452068;margin-bottom:8px;}
.section-desc{font-size:15px;color:#6b7280;line-height:1.7;}

/* TOOLS GRID */
.tools-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:20px;margin-bottom:56px;}

.tool-card{background:white;border-radius:20px;box-shadow:0 2px 20px rgba(69,32,104,0.08);overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #f0ecf8;transition:transform 0.2s,box-shadow 0.2s;}
.tool-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(69,32,104,0.15);}
.tool-card-top{padding:28px 28px 0;}
.tool-tag{display:inline-block;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:50px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;margin-bottom:14px;}
.tag-calculator{background:#f4eefa;color:#452068;}
.tag-guide{background:#f0fdf4;color:#16a34a;}
.tag-tool{background:#fff0f8;color:#ff1090;}
.tag-program{background:#fffbeb;color:#92400e;}
.tool-icon{font-size:36px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.tool-title{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#452068;margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.3;}
.tool-desc{font-size:14px;color:#6b7280;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:20px;}
.tool-card-bottom{padding:0 28px 28px;}
.tool-btn{display:block;text-align:center;background:#452068;color:white;padding:13px 20px;border-radius:50px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;transition:background 0.2s;}
.tool-btn:hover{background:#311549;}
.tool-btn.pink{background:#ff1090;}
.tool-btn.pink:hover{background:#cc0070;}
.tool-btn.outline{background:white;color:#452068;border:2px solid #452068;}
.tool-btn.outline:hover{background:#f4eefa;}

/* FEATURED CARD */
.tool-card.featured{border:2px solid #452068;position:relative;}
.featured-badge{position:absolute;top:-1px;right:24px;background:#ff1090;color:white;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:0 0 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.05em;}

/* GUIDES GRID */
.guides-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:16px;margin-bottom:56px;}
.guide-card{background:white;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(69,32,104,0.06);border:1px solid #f0ecf8;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;transition:transform 0.2s;}
.guide-card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);}
.guide-tag{display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:50px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;background:#f4eefa;color:#452068;width:fit-content;}
.guide-title{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a2e;line-height:1.4;}
.guide-desc{font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;line-height:1.6;flex:1;}
.guide-link{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#ff1090;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;}
.guide-link:hover{text-decoration:underline;}

/* FINAL CTA */
.final-cta{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#311549,#452068);border-radius:24px;padding:48px 40px;text-align:center;}
.final-cta-title{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:700;color:white;margin-bottom:12px;}
.final-cta-desc{font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:28px;max-width:520px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;}
.final-cta-btns{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.btn-pink-lg{display:inline-block;background:#ff1090;color:white;padding:15px 32px;border-radius:50px;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(255,16,144,0.35);}
.btn-white-lg{display:inline-block;background:white;color:#452068;padding:15px 32px;border-radius:50px;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;}

/* FOOTER */
footer{background:#1a1a2e;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);padding:40px 24px;text-align:center;font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;}
footer a{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);}
footer strong{color:white;}

@media(max-width:600px){
  .header{padding:0 16px;}
  .breadcrumb{padding:12px 16px;}
  .topbar{padding:8px 16px;}
  .topbar-lang{display:none;}
  .hero{padding:48px 20px 70px;}
  .final-cta{padding:32px 24px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-left">
    <a href="tel:18003806821" class="topbar-phone">&#9990; 1-800-380-6821</a>
    <span class="topbar-lang">English &amp; Spanish</span>
  </div>
  <div class="topbar-right">
    <a href="https://wa.me/13054646888" target="_blank" class="btn-wa">
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347z"/><path d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 2.123.556 4.116 1.526 5.845L0 24l6.335-1.508A11.945 11.945 0 0012 24c6.627 0 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm0 21.818a9.818 9.818 0 01-5.006-1.368l-.359-.214-3.728.887.916-3.636-.234-.374A9.818 9.818 0 1112 21.818z"/></svg>
      WhatsApp
    </a>
    <a href="https://calendly.com/healthexps-info/" target="_blank" class="btn-consult">Schedule Free Consultation &rarr;</a>
    <div class="lang-wrap">
      <button class="lb active" onclick="window.location.href='/resources'">EN</button>
      <button class="lb" onclick="window.location.href='/es/recursos'">ES</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<header class="header">
  <a href="/" class="brand">
    <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="The Health Experts Insurance" onerror="this.style.display='none';document.getElementById('bf').style.display='block'">
    <span id="bf" style="display:none;" class="brand-fallback">The Health Experts Insurance</span>
  </a>
  <a href="tel:18003806821" class="header-phone">
    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.01 15.38c-1.23 0-2.42-.2-3.53-.56-.35-.12-.74-.03-1.01.24l-1.57 1.97c-2.83-1.35-5.48-3.9-6.89-6.83l1.95-1.66c.27-.28.35-.67.24-1.02-.37-1.12-.56-2.3-.56-3.53 0-.54-.45-.99-.99-.99H4.19C3.65 3 3 3.24 3 3.99 3 13.28 10.73 21 20.01 21c.71 0 .99-.63.99-1.18v-3.45c0-.54-.45-.99-.99-.99z"/></svg>
    1-800-380-6821
  </a>
</header>

<div class="breadcrumb">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span>&rsaquo;</span>Resources
</div>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">Free Medicare Tools &middot; 2026</div>
  <h1>Free Tools &amp; Resources<br>to Make <em>Medicare Simple</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Calculators, guides, and plan comparison tools built by licensed Florida Medicare brokers — bilingual, free, no signup required.</p>
</div>

<div class="main">

  <!-- CALCULATORS -->
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Free Calculators</div>
    <div class="section-title">Run the numbers before you decide</div>
    <div class="section-desc">These tools take 2–3 minutes and can save you thousands in penalties, wrong plans, or missed benefits.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tools-grid">

    <div class="tool-card featured">
      <div class="featured-badge">Most Popular</div>
      <div class="tool-card-top">
        <div class="tool-tag tag-calculator">Calculator</div>
        <div class="tool-icon">⚖️</div>
        <div class="tool-title">Medicare Advantage vs. Supplement Cost Comparison</div>
        <div class="tool-desc">See your total projected costs at 1, 5, 10, and 20 years. Enter your age, plan premiums, and how much you use healthcare — and we show you which option costs less over time.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card-bottom">
        <a href="/medigap-calculator" class="tool-btn pink">Compare my costs &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top">
        <div class="tool-tag tag-calculator">Calculator</div>
        <div class="tool-icon">📅</div>
        <div class="tool-title">Medicare Enrollment Window Calculator</div>
        <div class="tool-desc">Find your exact IEP or SEP enrollment dates. Missing your window means a permanent penalty — enter your birthday or coverage end date and know exactly when to act.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card-bottom">
        <a href="/enrollment-calculator" class="tool-btn">Find my window &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top">
        <div class="tool-tag tag-calculator">Calculator</div>
        <div class="tool-icon">💰</div>
        <div class="tool-title">IRMAA Surcharge Calculator</div>
        <div class="tool-desc">Higher income means higher Part B and Part D premiums. See exactly how much you'll pay in 2026 based on your income — and learn if you can appeal your IRMAA.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card-bottom">
        <a href="/irmaa-calculator" class="tool-btn">Calculate my premium &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- TOOLS -->
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Plan Comparison Tools</div>
    <div class="section-title">Compare plans in your ZIP code</div>
    <div class="section-desc">See real plans available in South Florida — filter by doctors, medications, and budget.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tools-grid">

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top">
        <div class="tool-tag tag-tool">Plan Finder</div>
        <div class="tool-icon">🔍</div>
        <div class="tool-title">Medicare Plan Finder</div>
        <div class="tool-desc">Compare Medicare Advantage, Supplement, and Part D plans available in your ZIP code. Add your doctors and medications for accurate cost estimates. Powered by Sunfire.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card-bottom">
        <a href="/medicare-plan-finder" class="tool-btn pink">Find plans in my ZIP &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top">
        <div class="tool-tag tag-tool">Quiz</div>
        <div class="tool-icon">✅</div>
        <div class="tool-title">Which Plan Is Right for Me?</div>
        <div class="tool-desc">Answer 5 quick questions about your health, budget, and doctors. We'll tell you whether Medicare Advantage or Medigap makes more sense for your situation.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card-bottom">
        <a href="/find-my-plan" class="tool-btn">Take the quiz &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-card-top">
        <div class="tool-tag tag-program">Program</div>
        <div class="tool-icon">🏛️</div>
        <div class="tool-title">Medicare Savings Program</div>
        <div class="tool-desc">Florida may pay your Part B premium ($185/mo) and more if you qualify for MSP. Many people are surprised they qualify. Check in 2 minutes — free.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card-bottom">
        <a href="/medicare-savings-program" class="tool-btn outline">Check my eligibility &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- GUIDES -->
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Medicare Guides</div>
    <div class="section-title">Learn before you decide</div>
    <div class="section-desc">Plain-language guides written by licensed Florida brokers — no jargon, no sales pitch.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="guides-grid">
    <div class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-tag">Basics</div>
      <div class="guide-title">What is Medicare?</div>
      <div class="guide-desc">The four parts explained in plain English — A, B, C, D — and how they work together.</div>
      <a href="/medicare/what-is-medicare" class="guide-link">Read guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-tag">Enrollment</div>
      <div class="guide-title">Medicare Enrollment Periods</div>
      <div class="guide-desc">IEP, AEP, SEP, OEP, GEP — all the windows explained so you never miss yours.</div>
      <a href="/medicare-enrollment-periods" class="guide-link">Read guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-tag">Plans</div>
      <div class="guide-title">Medicare Advantage in Miami</div>
      <div class="guide-desc">How Part C works, HMO vs PPO, extra benefits, and top carriers in South Florida.</div>
      <a href="/medicare-advantage-miami" class="guide-link">Read guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-tag">Plans</div>
      <div class="guide-title">Medicare Supplement (Medigap)</div>
      <div class="guide-desc">Plan G vs Plan N, how Medigap fills the gaps, and what it costs in Florida.</div>
      <a href="/medicare-supplement-miami" class="guide-link">Read guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-tag">Costs</div>
      <div class="guide-title">Medicare Costs &amp; IRMAA</div>
      <div class="guide-desc">Premiums, deductibles, and income-based surcharges — what you'll actually pay in 2026.</div>
      <a href="/medicare/medicare-costs-irmaa" class="guide-link">Read guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-tag">Myths</div>
      <div class="guide-title">15 Medicare Myths</div>
      <div class="guide-desc">Common misconceptions that cost Florida seniors thousands — debunked with facts.</div>
      <a href="/medicare-myths" class="guide-link">Read guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-tag">Savings</div>
      <div class="guide-title">Medicare Savings Program</div>
      <div class="guide-desc">How Florida can pay your Part B premium and more — QMB, SLMB, and QI explained.</div>
      <a href="/medicare-savings-program" class="guide-link">Read guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-tag">Insurance</div>
      <div class="guide-title">Compare Medicare Plans Miami</div>
      <div class="guide-desc">Side-by-side comparison of all plan types available to South Florida residents.</div>
      <a href="/medicare-plans-miami" class="guide-link">Read guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <div class="final-cta">
    <div class="final-cta-title">Still not sure which option is right for you?</div>
    <p class="final-cta-desc">Our licensed bilingual brokers in Doral, FL compare all plans for you — free. We check your doctors, your medications, and your budget. No cost, no obligation, ever.</p>
    <div class="final-cta-btns">
      <a href="https://calendly.com/healthexps-info/" target="_blank" class="btn-pink-lg">Schedule free consultation &rarr;</a>
      <a href="tel:18003806821" class="btn-white-lg">Call 1-800-380-6821</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<footer>
  <strong>The Health Experts Insurance</strong><br>
